  "prompt": "What is the best Instagram followers tracking app?",
  "response": "There are several apps available that are popular for tracking Instagram followers. The \"best\" app can depend on your specific needs, such as ease of use, features, and budget. Here are a few highly regarded options:\n\n1. **Followers Analyzer for Instagram**: This app provides detailed insights into your followers, including who has unfollowed you, who doesn\u2019t follow you back, and who you don\u2019t follow back.\n\n2. **Follower Insight for Instagram**: Offers similar features with a focus on tracking unfollowers, mutual followers, and more.\n\n3. **Iconosquare**: Known for its robust analytics, Iconosquare provides detailed data on follower growth, engagement metrics, and account comparison.\n\n4. **Hootsuite**: While primarily known as a social media management tool, Hootsuite offers insights and analytics for Instagram, including follower tracking.\n\n5. **Social Blade**: Provides an overview of your Instagram follower count over time, along with engagement statistics.\n\n6. **Crowdfire**: Besides managing your follow/unfollow activity, Crowdfire also suggests content you can post to increase engagement.\n\nWhen selecting an app, consider checking user reviews, evaluating the pricing structure, and ensuring the app supports the features you require. Always be cautious of apps that ask for too much personal information or require unusual permissions.",
